ll review your application against the eligibility criteria and you will receive a decision within a few weeks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once your application is approved, we will work with you to prepare your cancer research portfolio for upload, introduce you to the partnership and <a href=\"/user/register\" style=\"font-weight:bold\">register</a> your ICRP representatives. Please note that we can only give access to the partner database once your first data upload has been received.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n'
  where entity_id = 19;

